    "description": "Immerse yourself in a massive open-world ski resort like never before in Ski Patrol! With stunning landscapes created using real-world elevation data, Ski Patrol is the ultimate skiing experience for thrill-seekers and explorers alike.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\nDynamic Open World<br />\r\n<br />\r\nSki across vast mountains, tackling objectives such as rescuing injured skiers, mitigating avalanche hazards, discovering hidden huts, and tracking down trail markers to learn about your surroundings.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\nTotal Freedom<br />\r\n<br />\r\nWhether you're completing objectives or just throwing yourself off cliffs for the adrenaline rush, the choice is yours. Every nook and cranny has something new to uncover, and it all starts with a ride up the lift.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\nRealistic Ski Physics<br />\r\n<br />\r\nControl your skis with precision using your mouse. Learn to carve turns, perform hockey stops, or just bomb straight down the slope. How you ski is up to you! <br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\nProgression System<br />\r\n<br />\r\nEarn cash by completing goals and use it to unlock new maps, expanding your adventure to fresh, breathtaking locations.",
